{
  "stem": "22840.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the-- the numbers are documented very well in those memoirs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, it's part of the archives of Yad Vashem.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in Nove Mesto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there were no-- no Germans in Nove Mesto, to the best of my recollection.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall any German from Nove Meso And indeed, the-- and the German army really invaded, in force, into Slovakia, only at the opposite-- onset, not opposite-- the onset of the Slovak National Uprising.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44 That was in 1944.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say it was clear of trouble.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was clear of Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were the Hlinka Guard, which was the Slovak equivalent of the SA, I would say, or the SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were clearly visible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was clear that I should avoid them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody should avoid them, as much as one can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were Slovak gatherings that we had to avoid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From my recollection, or from my knowledge?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, from my recollection as a child, the only thing I can tell you is being beaten by-- by the gentiles, so to speak, having no recourse to help, of any adult on the street.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If there was an adult, he or she would not interfere, clearly not on my behalf.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From my knowledge, the rules, the-- the legislature in Slovakia, was following pretty much a Nuremberg legislature.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were willing participants.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have quotes from Tiso.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tiso was the leader of Slovakia [? then. ?] I would not call him the Fuhrer of Slovakia, but he was the leader of Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a Catholic priest.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there are many quotes from him, supporting the legislature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was clearly a willing participant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His government was full of willing participants.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was clear economic value, to the Slovaks, in depriving the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
